					<description><![CDATA[惊蛰过后，天气渐渐变暖，如果说有什么水果不能错过，菠萝一定算一个！ 菠萝是春季“黄金果” 酸甜多汁的菠萝除了味 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">惊蛰过后，天气渐渐变暖，如果说有什么水果不能错过，菠萝一定算一个！</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">菠萝是春季“黄金果”</span></span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">酸甜多汁的菠萝除了味道美，还有极高的营养价值和药用价值。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">中医认为菠萝性平，味甘微酸，多归脾、胃、肾经。《本草纲目》记载，菠萝能</span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">“补脾胃，固元气，制伏元阳，扶持衰土，壮精神。益血，宽脾，消痰，解酒毒，止酒后发渴。”</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">简单来说，就是菠萝能够</span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">健脾养胃、益气消食！</span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">尤其是对于春季容易出现积食、胃口不佳的老人和孩子而言。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">而从现代医学的角度来看，它的营养价值也很是不错。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">01、</span></span><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">促进消化</span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">菠萝所含的蛋白质酶可以分解蛋白质，增加肠胃蠕动助消化，对便秘有一定疗效。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">平时，在大鱼大肉后吃片菠萝，可以预防脂肪沉积，对身体大有好处。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">02、</span></span><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">消除疲劳</span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">而其甜中带酸的口感，能够刺激唾液分泌，其中富含维生素B1，能促进身体新陈代谢，消除疲劳感，让你在整个春天都精力焕发。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">03、</span></span><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">保护血管</span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">更值得一提的是，菠萝中所含的“菠萝朊酶”能分解蛋白质，能帮助溶解阻塞于组织中的纤维蛋白和血凝块，改善局部血液循环，对于保护中老年人的血管健康也有很大帮助。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">04、</span></span><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">提高免疫力</span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">同时，菠萝含有多种维生素、矿物质，特别富含维生素C和锰，这对于强健身体有好处；另一方面，菠萝富含<strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">类黄酮和酚酸类抗氧化剂，</span></strong>能抵御自由基，减少炎症，强化免疫系统。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">所以说，菠萝是名副其实的“春季黄金果”。</span></span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/e027f1f1462e63073e953fcc65fb77b5.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">吃菠萝有禁忌</span></strong></span></span></p><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">过敏的不能吃；</span></span></span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">吃萝卜的时候尽量不吃菠萝；</span></span></span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">在吃铁剂补充剂的时候，尽量不吃菠萝；</span></span></span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">吃药的时候，包括中药和西药，尽量不吃菠萝；</span></span></span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">不要跟牛奶一起吃，尽量隔开1~2小时；</span></span></span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">菠萝有酸性，会刺激牙龈、黏膜，有口腔溃疡的最好不吃；</span></span></span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">菠萝酸味强劲，患低血压、内脏下垂的人应尽量少吃；</span></span></span>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">挑菠萝有技巧</span></span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">平时，我们在选购菠萝时，最好是现买现削，尽量不要买已经削好并在塑料袋中包装完毕的。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">这类菠萝存在放置过久的问题，可能有一定的卫生隐患。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">那么，我们如何买到一个可口的菠萝呢？</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">01、</span></span><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">看外观形状</span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">优质较好的菠萝呈圆柱形或两头稍尖的椭圆形，大小均匀适中，果形端正，芽眼数量少。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">02、</span></span><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">看外观颜色</span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">菠萝颜色呈淡黄色或亮黄色的可直接食用，颜色淡黄色，微带青绿光泽的，这样的一般是八分熟，如果是当天吃可买外观是淡黄色的，如果需要过两天吃的可选微带青绿光泽的。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">03、</span></span><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">摸外观硬度</span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">用手轻轻按压菠萝，坚硬而无弹性的是生菠萝；挺实而微微软的是成熟度较好的；过陷甚至凹陷者为成熟过度的菠萝；如果有汁液溢出则说明果实已经变质。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">04、</span></span><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">用鼻嗅</span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">用鼻子闻菠萝香味，未成熟的菠萝闻起来没有什么味道，外面淡淡清香的，切开后香气扑鼻的是成熟的菠萝，外表皮就有很浓香气的菠萝说明成熟过了。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">05、</span></span><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">看果肉</span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">切开后，良质菠萝的果目浅而小，内部呈淡黄色组织致密，果肉厚而果芯细小，劣质菠萝果目深而多，有的果目可深达菠萝芯，内部组织空隙大，果肉薄而果芯粗大，如果是未成熟的菠萝果肉比较脆，且颜色有些白。</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">小贴士：菠萝煮一煮，口感更好。</span></span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">很多人生吃菠萝会感觉口唇刺痛，其实，这与菠萝过敏有关。</span></span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">防止吃菠萝过敏最简单的方法是把</span></span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">菠萝煮熟，或者用开水泡几分钟。</span></span></strong></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">因为导致过敏的菠萝蛋白酶最佳活性温度是50~60℃左右，高温可以破坏其活性，也能让菠萝的保健功效更好地发挥出来。</span></span></span></span></p>


</p>
